# Shell Script Conventions

- Shell: **bash** (not sh, not zsh)
- First line: `#!/usr/bin/env bash`
- Second line: `set -euo pipefail`
- Indent: 2 spaces
- Quote all variables: `"${var}"` not `$var`
- Use `[[ ]]` instead of `[ ]`

## Script Locations

- Deploy/reset/health: `infra/scripts/`
- Monitoring: `scripts/monitoring/` (if legacy)
- Setup/provisioning: `scripts/setup/` (if legacy)

## Key Scripts

```bash
bash infra/scripts/reset-lab.sh      # full lab reset
bash infra/scripts/health-check.sh   # check all services
```
